OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776700609
OL,3,CWife of dad killed in Soho Road crash
OL,4,Csays her life has changed forever
OL,6,FThe wife of a father who was killed in
OL,7,Fa collision in Birmingham earlier this
OL,8,Fyear says her life has changed forever
OL,9,Ffollowing his death and that she has
OL,10,F"lost her soulmate".
OL,12,FHizar Hanif died after an Audi A4
OL,13,Fploughed into the back of the car he
OL,14,Fwas travelling in on 18 February this
OL,15,Fyear, in Soho Road.
OL,17,FMr Hanif and his friend were preparing
OL,18,Ffor his friend's wedding the following
OL,19,Fweek and were travelling to another
OL,20,Ffriend's house to collect suits when
OL,21,Fthey were hit by the car.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776700609
OL,3,CWife of dad killed in Soho Road crash
OL,4,Csays her life has changed forever
OL,6,FMr Hanif died at the scene and his
OL,7,Ffriend suffered minor physical
OL,8,Finjuries.
OL,10,FMohammed Ali has now been jailed for
OL,11,Fthe incident, after he drove his car
OL,12,Fat speeds of up to 90mph in Soho Road,
OL,13,Fwhere he was also seen dangerously
OL,14,Fovertaking other cars before hitting
OL,15,Fthe car Mr Hanif was travelling in.
OL,17,FA statement from Mr Hanif's wife was
OL,18,Fread out in court where she described
OL,19,Fher husband as "the heart of our
OL,20,Ffamily".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776700609
OL,3,CWife of dad killed in Soho Road crash
OL,4,Csays her life has changed forever
OL,6,FIt reads: "That day my life changed
OL,7,Fforever. I lost my soulmate, my son
OL,8,Flost his daddy, his parents lost a son
OL,9,Fand his brothers lost their big
OL,10,Fbrother.
OL,12,F"I don't understand how one minute
OL,13,Flife was perfect, and then it wasn't.
OL,14,FThis should never have happened. I
OL,15,Fhave no peace and I'm living on
OL,16,Fautopilot.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776700609
OL,3,CWife of dad killed in Soho Road crash
OL,4,Csays her life has changed forever
OL,6,F"My son didn't have enough time with
OL,7,Fhis daddy and that's not ok. No child
OL,8,Fshould have to experience grief so
OL,9,Fyoung. I am struggling to figure out
OL,10,Fhow i live in a world without him
OL,11,Fbeside me.
OL,13,F"Hizar was everything to our family. A
OL,14,Floving husband, a devoted father, son,
OL,15,Fbrother and the heart of our family.
OL,16,FHis loss is something we will carry
OL,17,Fwith us for the rest of our lives."
OL,19,FPolice said Ali also collided with
OL,20,Fanother car, seriously injuring the
OL,21,Fdriver.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776700609
OL,3,CWife of dad killed in Soho Road crash
OL,4,Csays her life has changed forever
OL,6,FAli was taken to hospital where he
OL,7,Falso verbally and physically assaulted
OL,8,Fa police officer.
OL,10,FHe was arrested and later charged with
OL,11,Fcausing death by dangerous driving,
OL,12,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,13,Fdriving and assaulting a police
OL,14,Fofficer.
OL,16,FThe 27-year-old pleaded guilty at
OL,17,FBirmingham Crown Court. He's now been
OL,18,Fsentenced to seven years in prison and
OL,19,Fbanned from driving for four years and
OL,20,Fsix months on release.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
